      "rationale": "Eleven non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs were assembled from a single production lot, dimensionally inspected, and tested at two independent laboratories (FDA CDRH and DePuy Synthes). Inter-laboratory coefficient of variation for stiffness was 3.2%, confirming adequate sample representativeness for Gradation 3."
