      "rationale": "Testing was performed under a single ASTM F1717 static compression-bending configuration. Although the protocol is standardized, only one test condition (no variation in load angle or offset) was evaluated, limiting this factor to Gradation 2, one level below the required Gradation 3. This is a documented limitation accepted by the assessment team."
