      "rationale": "For all three QoIs (stiffness, yield force, force at 40 mm), E/uval ranged from 0.31 to 1.44 and percentage differences ranged from 1.2% to 8.7%, all within acceptance bounds. Output comparison satisfies Gradation 3."
